OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781187095
OL,3,COne year on from Air India crash: sole
OL,4,Csurvivor calls for answers
OL,6,FSome 169 Indian passengers and 52
OL,7,FBritish nationals were killed, making
OL,8,Fit one of the deadliest plane crashes
OL,9,Fin terms of the number of British
OL,10,Ffatalities.
OL,12,FMr Ramesh previously said the death of
OL,13,Fhis brother Ajay "took all my
OL,14,Fhappiness" after describing it as a
OL,15,F"miracle" that he survived.
OL,17,FIn a statement 12 months on from the
OL,18,Fcrash, he said: "What many people
OL,19,Fperhaps don't fully appreciate is that
OL,20,Fthe trauma didn't end on the day of
OL,21,Fthe disaster.
OL,26,@uD@ROUvD@JO]wD@AOUwD@IO]zD@QOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781187095
OL,3,COne year on from Air India crash: sole
OL,4,Csurvivor calls for answers
OL,6,F"I live with the significant
OL,7,Fpsychological scars, the loss of my
OL,8,Fbrother, and the constant unanswered
OL,9,Fquestions around how and why this
OL,10,Fhappened.
OL,12,F"I know those questions are not just
OL,13,Fon my mind ` they are on the minds of
OL,14,Fevery affected family.
OL,16,F"More than anything, people need
OL,17,Fhonesty, transparency and answers.
OL,18,FNothing will ever change what
OL,19,Fhappened, but families deserve
OL,20,Fclarity."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781187095
OL,3,COne year on from Air India crash: sole
OL,4,Csurvivor calls for answers
OL,6,FInvestigators have yet to publish
OL,7,Ftheir final findings into the cause of
OL,8,Fthe crash.
OL,10,FA preliminary report into the incident
OL,11,Ffrom India's Aircraft Accident
OL,12,FInvestigation Bureau found both of the
OL,13,Fplane's fuel switches moved to the
OL,14,F"cut-off" position "immediately" after
OL,15,Ftake-off, stopping fuel supply to the
OL,16,Fengine.
OL,18,FMr Ramesh met with Air Accident
OL,19,FInvestigators in Ahmedabad in March,
OL,20,Fhis representative Sanjiv Patel said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@IO]vD@TOUvD@`O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781187095
OL,3,COne year on from Air India crash: sole
OL,4,Csurvivor calls for answers
OL,6,FMr Patel said the crash survivor has
OL,7,Fto date received #21,500 from Air
OL,8,FIndia to support his wife and five-
OL,9,Fyear-old son ` an interim payment
OL,10,Fprovided to all families who lost
OL,11,Floved ones in the disaster.
OL,13,FMr Ramesh is taking civil action
OL,14,Ffollowing the crash, with his
OL,15,Fsolicitors saying: "We will be
OL,16,Fexamining every detail of the air
OL,17,Faccident investigations and expecting
OL,18,Fall parties involved to act
OL,19,Fappropriately to any findings of
OL,20,Ffault, failure or negligence."
OL,26,@wD@TOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781187095
OL,3,COne year on from Air India crash: sole
OL,4,Csurvivor calls for answers
OL,6,FSolicitor Paul McClorry from Hudgell
OL,7,FSolicitors said civil claims are being
OL,8,Fconsidered against a number of
OL,9,Fpotential defendants.
OL,11,FHe said in a statement: "We've had
OL,12,Fsignificant dialogue with the legal
OL,13,Frepresentatives for Air India and they
OL,14,Fhave been very cooperative in recent
OL,15,Ftimes, providing some initial funding
OL,16,Ffor much needed physical and
OL,17,Fpsychological rehabilitation support.
OL,26,@sD@YOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781187095
OL,3,COne year on from Air India crash: sole
OL,4,Csurvivor calls for answers
OL,6,F"We are awaiting the findings of the
OL,7,Finvestigations, and we should finally
OL,8,Fstart to see some clarity as to how
OL,9,Fand why this awful disaster happened,
OL,10,Fand, crucially, how it could have been
OL,11,Favoided.
OL,13,F"Lessons clearly must be learnt, and
OL,14,Ffor that to happen there needs to be
OL,15,Fcomplete transparency and a
OL,16,Fwillingness to accept responsibility."
OL,18,FThe Foreign Office have been
OL,19,Fapproached for comment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
