CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781187095
OL,3,COne year on from Air India crash: sole
OL,4,Csurvivor calls for answers
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Air India said:
OL,7,F"Air India remains committed to
OL,8,Fsupporting every individual impacted
OL,9,Fby the AI171 tragedy with care and
OL,10,Fcompassion. While we cannot discuss
OL,11,Fthe specifics of any individual case,
OL,12,Frepresentatives from Air India and the
OL,13,FTata Group met with Mr Ramesh and had
OL,14,Fa constructive and meaningful
OL,15,Fengagement.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781187095
OL,3,COne year on from Air India crash: sole
OL,4,Csurvivor calls for answers
OL,6,F"The discussions provided insight into
OL,7,FMr Ramesh's needs and concerns,
OL,8,Fenabling a clearer understanding of
OL,9,Fhow best to support him. We remain in
OL,10,Fclose contact with Mr Ramesh and his
OL,11,Frepresentatives and are actively
OL,12,Fworking to ensure that appropriate
OL,13,Fsupport continues to be extended to
OL,14,Fhim."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@EO]
